<li><strong>Business type and size:</strong> Your industry, sales volume, and average transaction size can all impact your rates.</li>
<li><strong>Card type:</strong> Different types of cards (like rewards cards or corporate cards) can carry different rates.</li>
</ul>

For the most accurate information, it''s best to directly contact Clearent or visit their website. Don''t forget to ask about any additional fees, like PCI compliance fees, chargeback fees, or monthly minimums!

