INSERT INTO public.messages VALUES ('10cfb2a6-caf9-4da4-9120-c2418bc03419', '8839ecc2-0386-46cb-ac1e-073ae04f175a', 'Hey, payment processing rates are essentially the fees that businesses pay to facilitate the transactions between themselves and their customers. They vary depending on a number of factors. Here''s a quick rundown:

<h3>Key Factors Influencing Payment Processing Rates:</h3>
<ul>
<li><strong>Transaction volume:</strong> The more transactions a business processes, the lower the rate they might be able to negotiate.</li>
<li><strong>Card type:</strong> Different types of cards (credit, debit, rewards) can have different rates.</li>
<li><strong>Processing method:</strong> Whether the card is swiped, inserted, or manually entered can affect the rate.</li>
<li><strong>Merchant''s industry:</strong> Some industries are considered higher risk, which may result in higher rates.</li>
</ul>

